{"tid":1788181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人聲明: 香港人從無提出黃店逼捐錢同分級制","createTime":"2019-12-18T12:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T21:40:28.000Z","uid":17510,"like":263,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"be44c68661440d82a14ba18c72f21354350d0cf2","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"老老實實，依啲咁既概念同共匪文革批鬥一啲分別都無。<br />\n我地香港人從來都只係想盡最大努力去爭取一眾商店加入並壯大黃色經濟圈。一切逼人捐錢、分級制度，只係港共同中共分化技倆，作為香港人，我地必須認清敵人技倆並與之割席"},{"pid":"724d8881095c01be3ac47af24a2e6ba7fa636c50","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:08:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8267141e0c20a5e222ee8d13250cccdbfeb134c","tid":1788181,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b45daf8be34c88f49ed60b8805d8eaa48bba0375","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"其實依啲所謂分級制度同逼人捐錢<br />\n一定係共匪搵人帶風向吹出黎<br />\n我唔係鳩up<br />\n<br />\n就好似點解我地對國民教育、國歌法咁反感一樣<br />\n原因係佢地連我地應該點樣去愛國既型式都要規範埋，你唔跟佢果套就係錯<br />\n<br />\n喂？同你逼人捐錢有乜分別？<br />\n你唔捐錢比前線、即使你捐左你唔大大聲話比我聽你捐左錢，你都係未夠支持，所以你係低級黃店<br />\n<br />\n依啲擺到明就係共匪式思維，我絕對唔相信我地香港人會諗得出依啲自己最討厭既政策出黎規範自己人<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一可以做既就係每次見到依啲有機會做成內部分化言論既時候都即時割席。"},{"pid":"f95c807d01efafc2722b7d02f24490f0ebc3dffa","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8267141e0c20a5e222ee8d13250cccdbfeb134c","tid":1788181,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b93c9851fb1cb1f1bcc6f5f357b469cefd8b66","tid":1788181,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"自由社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf4fb0abbe0693a92ff12fd3851d94a47b4e2d5","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a6b93c9851fb1cb1f1bcc6f5f357b469cefd8b66","tid":1788181,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"自由社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"我地只係需要黃藍歸邊<br />\n依條亦係我地底線<br />\n<br />\n至於人地支持黃色經濟圈支持到乜嘢程度就佢地自己選擇"},{"pid":"6f514cbc37fc054fcc9cdb84e3f33d2a5ca527e6","tid":1788181,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"65bdc6749f51515c7f153039b0ccb9dddb2007a9","tid":1788181,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"有遊行幫我地貼文宣，其實好夠"},{"pid":"94b88b3f46b7d35053a7adf2b3ac775930f5b9fb","tid":1788181,"uid":65747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"無錯 , 逼捐乜撚野姐 , 屌你老尾藍絲呀"},{"pid":"f45070e78c7b7bf319b9683c389ac92c8f296719","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"我依個post並唔係帶領大家捉鬼<br />\n而係希望大家能夠意志堅定<br />\n認清自己底線同目的係乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n只要你自己意志夠堅定，即使出面再大風都吹你唔郁"},{"pid":"7ae98ca83a624bd051914cd4a23880b3655d2cfc","tid":1788181,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"不可以對黃店要求太高，反而要儘量多舖頭變黃"},{"pid":"2d224f65f7cb8111c93f920bf96f8ca8ca648889","tid":1788181,"uid":13308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"唔反已經多謝<br />\n支持既話我地更加應該大力支持<br />\n唔需要有咩要求人地<br />\n我覺得公義同民族性唔應該用錢黎衡量"},{"pid":"d70209ea2e94a32155d37f6cf2585615998e4a2c","tid":1788181,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"0eb8e4b6fa7af8d871dfe95b2c53eb1a7d7dbf59","tid":1788181,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d362387a0198cd780a5809fd63823b124a0e62be","tid":1788181,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e23e8ffcae8c6df95e9cfddecd81b0114d34208","tid":1788181,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"其實貼文宣真係已經好夠"},{"pid":"b3d7831bf5425775dc3dfe2fcdc44836a372853f","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b88b3f46b7d35053a7adf2b3ac775930f5b9fb","tid":1788181,"uid":65747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"無錯 , 逼捐乜撚野姐 , 屌你老尾藍絲呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"我地見到既話就要面斥不雅<br />\n<br />\n一係佢係本身係黃比共匪影響左所以誤入歧途<br />\n一係就係真共匪抓牙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我地都要本著不分化既原則，只須當面斥責該行為就夠，而唔好去標籤依啲係咪黃絲所為"},{"pid":"97b3fd7947956d620a887494b8f041666267b242","tid":1788181,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈原意應該係俾消費者知邊間店嘅老闆支持場運動，等消費者去幫襯，而唔係逼黃店捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126a7afc75f15ae660291b84d38d0f48bf75d000","tid":1788181,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"新式五毛係好撚精<br />\n<br />\n<ins>故意扮自己人攪到所有野陳義過高</ins><br />\n<br />\n例如:黃店扣完開支要盡捐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問老細係咪唔洗養家<br />\n<br />\n故意迫人做義工係打擊緊抗爭的可持續性"},{"pid":"58309b2780061b0b3c6025b5626eeb347f13df5e","tid":1788181,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c640e1f5d56bf2ee11cffd1c57e86fd1cd09d485","tid":1788181,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c921c2b268b006b214b51dca89b19b2c88197fad","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"126a7afc75f15ae660291b84d38d0f48bf75d000","tid":1788181,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"新式五毛係好撚精<br />\n<br />\n<ins>故意扮自己人攪到所有野陳義過高</ins><br />\n<br />\n例如:黃店扣完開支要盡捐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問老細係咪唔洗養家<br />\n<br />\n故意迫人做義工係打擊緊抗爭的可持續性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"我都係咁認為<br />\n所以我地一定要出聲<br />\n<br />\n但係爭論既時候我地卻要注意避免標籤對方<br />\n因為你永遠唔會知道對方係真心膠定係假膠<br />\n<br />\n如果係一個一直都支持開黃但係比我地標籤左佢<br />\n可能佢會心灰意冷從而我地會少咁一個手足<br />\n達到左班假膠同三毛既分化目的<br />\n<br />\n我地只可以盡力去拉返對方重返正途"},{"pid":"d3173871e1dc9b2ea54d659e5743615cc6021d5e","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c640e1f5d56bf2ee11cffd1c57e86fd1cd09d485","tid":1788181,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"再推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad009979421d1e57379f084d6a217c60ceaed79d","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d224f65f7cb8111c93f920bf96f8ca8ca648889","tid":1788181,"uid":13308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"唔反已經多謝<br />\n支持既話我地更加應該大力支持<br />\n唔需要有咩要求人地<br />\n我覺得公義同民族性唔應該用錢黎衡量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"同意   就同做善事一樣"},{"pid":"251bbd711caa160436030483877598991ff94027","tid":1788181,"uid":18208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"90f748a7b4839742ad8881b770e8b6b76b8dc114","tid":1788181,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b1fc211c059b999c91d96d7c1fc0e4a0ed36f53","tid":1788181,"uid":18208,"like":0,"d