gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9887db8421dd63b465345e319d732be4d1e231bb","tid":1788181,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"1640086e5c3fd3b42f03c3dd111f3987bc45dba2","tid":1788181,"uid":67465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯"},{"pid":"74bb610356e684d5786c978e16edbe1c4a52a776","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"最近睇左一段片<br />\n內容係講點解瑞典可以係一二戰都一直都咁犀利保持中立<br />\n<br />\n原因就只有一個<br />\n佢地由細到大都被灌輸以下一套思想：<br />\n任何既投降言論、失敗主義都只係敵人製造既輿論。<br />\n加上一套政治制度設計，就係政府並不能代表全國做出投降決定，亦即係同我地無大台一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地無大台已經做到<br />\n而家我地逼切既下一步就係鞏固黃色同埋和通不分既意識形態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd18a123e26e7d0fda1a51d6305521eaa10a800","tid":1788181,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74bb610356e684d5786c978e16edbe1c4a52a776","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"最近睇左一段片<br />\n內容係講點解瑞典可以係一二戰都一直都咁犀利保持中立<br />\n<br />\n原因就只有一個<br />\n佢地由細到大都被灌輸以下一套思想：<br />\n任何既投降言論、失敗主義都只係敵人製造既輿論。<br />\n加上一套政治制度設計，就係政府並不能代表全國做出投降決定，亦即係同我地無大台一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地無大台已經做到<br />\n而家我地逼切既下一步就係鞏固黃色同埋和通不分既意識形態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"證明失敗主義撚係on9"},{"pid":"c577326cbb9904a9b269eb3d6850d0c774f4cb59","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"li