=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"5bd212844825ab7f1f97ce294ddbcd2daf10135a","tid":1788181,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"佢哋不停放風抹黑 <br />\n因為黃色經濟圈是好致命的"},{"pid":"adba134370d3a95e2f9b0d26c618c5bdaf456498","tid":1788181,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"[檢討文]呢場運動經歷半年，想係度總結經驗同觀察，歡迎討論（整體）（預咗無人理）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ca3533f3e53f9687214f8d81cdcad0383a5bcfd","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd212844825ab7f1f97ce294ddbcd2daf10135a","tid":1788181,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"佢哋不停放風抹黑 <br />\n因為黃色經濟圈是好致命的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"佢地想我地失敗<br />\n但我地唔會認輸"},{"pid":"3e8d565b4af879625f3398b26f32527de294ddde","tid":1788181,"uid":273716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈要從寛<br />\n當務之急係做大個圈 唔係做黃個圈<br />\n分級制捐錢對深黃黎講當然好睇<br />\n但絕對會係阻礙圈子擴大<br />\nStandard太高只會令人灰心、邊緣化自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbdcba90455ea0fd07421c40d64e2debe7d20fb","tid":1788181,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45daf8be34c88f49ed60b8805d8eaa48bba0375","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"其實依啲所謂分級制度同逼人捐錢<br />\n一定係共匪搵人帶風向吹出黎<br />\n我唔係鳩up<br />\n<br />\n就好似點解我地對國民教育、國歌法咁反感一樣<br />\n原因係佢地連我地應該點樣去愛國既型式都要規範埋，你唔跟佢果套就係錯<br />\n<br />\n喂？同你逼人捐錢有乜分別？<br />\n你唔捐錢比前線、即使你捐左你唔大大聲話比我聽你捐左錢，你都係未夠支持，所以你係低級黃店<br />\n<br />\n依啲擺到明就係共匪式思維，我絕對唔相信我地香港人會諗得出依啲自己最討厭既政策出黎規範自己人<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一可以做既就係每次見到依啲有機會做成內部分化言論既時候都即時割席。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"同意呀 叫推黃店分級既仆街 分左自己級先"},{"pid":"76ff548f4be6d2dfc7581fd5e5e912aefa46fc30","tid":1788181,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27d8db7807b4af78f0454dccfdd0437db7308c7d","tid":1788181,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e6a2dbd004873fee2c38f6c46905f509cd09b6","tid":1788181,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"又要毛主席教你抗爭---「政治就是把自己的朋友搞得多多的，敵人的朋友搞得少少的」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785063</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a53b99e2190ec34cc6a0d012c1c22c7dbf24e3f5","tid":1788181,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e1f9a71d531729d0690a492712fc37fa16bb11","tid":1788181,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f1e498cbaa0f4c2eecea966fb93186bcb11ff88","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9b272e392ac87b40591387da8aec3a4cd2dca03","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8313e84f7cd1aacbabc69924bab18de7bbf8144b","tid":1788181,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b45daf8be34c88f49ed60b8805d8eaa48bba0375","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"其實依啲所謂分級制度同逼人捐錢<br />\n一定係共匪搵人帶風向吹出黎<br />\n我唔係鳩up<br />\n<br />\n就好似點解我地對國民教育、國歌法咁反感一樣<br />\n原因係佢地連我地應該點樣去愛國既型式都要規範埋，你唔跟佢果套就係錯<br />\n<br />\n喂？同你逼人捐錢有乜分別？<br />\n你唔捐錢比前線、即使你捐左你唔大大聲話比我聽你捐左錢，你都係未夠支持，所以你係低級黃店<br />\n<br />\n依啲擺到明就係共匪式思維，我絕對唔相信我地香港人會諗得出依啲自己最討厭既政策出黎規範自己人<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一可以做既就係每次見到依啲有機會做成內部分化言論既時候都即時割席。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:22:42.000Z","msg":"你同熱狗口徑一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97be592b0493e0bf7a5d37f44c96126c2554c27","tid":1788181,"uid":134445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:29:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dda9bbe63aac37fe2c76f46e8b526657223e3bd9","tid":1788181,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"咁一定要貼日程表同文宣呢？<br />\n唔出錢啫，幫手輸出革命都得掛<br />\n<br />\n又可以逼埋偽黃幫手輸出革命"},{"pid":"4315fbb1cfad5225a832e8667d5b72cd2fa90fa1","tid":1788181,"uid":312333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74bb610356e684d5786c978e16edbe1c4a52a776","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"最近睇左一段片<br />\n內容係講點解瑞典可以係一二戰都一直都咁犀利保持中立<br />\n<br />\n原因就只有一個<br />\n佢地由細到大都被灌輸以下一套思想：<br />\n任何既投降言論、失敗主義都只係敵人製造既輿論。<br />\n加上一套政治制度設計，就係政府並不能代表全國做出投降決定，亦即係同我地無大台一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地無大台已經做到<br />\n而家我地逼切既下一步就係鞏固黃色同埋和通不分既意識形態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:34:15.000Z","msg":"瑞士啊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"4bb312dab650ed64743631f74530c4418e394d26","tid":1788181,"uid":34616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff354022baf01f099adc5cc1b3e38883a70064a","tid":1788181,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:47:56.000Z","msg":"有啲基本野做下，例如唔播tvb/加一個另外既tip box for捐/忙得滯當獎金分比員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見有啲鋪多人到啲員工死下死下，好想tip佢地，另外加個盒仔應該多左人tip員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326531229424e8295d5c0755b3ca2e92ecb56513","tid":1788181,"uid":93431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T20:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36ae7a39e95c7a89ca94b2e71f30a8d7d40c3bd","tid":1788181,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T21:17:53.000Z","msg":"要分級不如幫藍店分級好過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f4ad57be31c12e376475c6339509d86819379e","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4315fbb1cfad5225a832e8667d5b72cd2fa90fa1","tid":1788181,"uid":312333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74bb610356e684d5786c978e16edbe1c4a52a776","tid":1788181,"uid":17510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime